Fourth Department,

January, 1963

(January 10, 1963) The People of the State of New York ex rel. Jacob Wissenfeld, Appellant, v. Walter H. Wilkins, as Warden of Attica Prison, Respondent.

Order unanimously affirmed, without costs of this appeal to either party. (Appeal from order of Wyoming County Court dismissing a writ of habeas corpus and remanding the relator to the custody of the Warden of Attica Prison.) Present — Williams, P. J., Bastow, Goldman, Halpern and MoClusky, JJ.
